  "description": "A close-up, top-down shot of a purple tulip in full bloom. The petals are a rich, deep purple, with subtle variations in tone. The interior of the flower reveals a complex structure: dark, almost black, central reproductive parts surrounded by orange-yellow stamens and pistils. The petals exhibit a slight curl, and the overall texture appears velvety. Green leaves are visible in the blurred background, indicating an outdoor setting. The lighting is soft and natural, highlighting the flower's delicate details.",
